Package me.masstrix.eternalnature.util

Class AbstractNumber

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.masstrix.eternalnature.util.AbstractNumber
  • public class AbstractNumber
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstracts arithmetic and some math operations to work for any number type. This is useful to use when you are not sure what the number type that will be used but need to do some arithmetic operations.
